              <li>âš›ï¸ <strong>Frameworks</strong>: React, Vue, Svelte, Angular, Next.js, and Astro</li>
              <li>ğŸ’» <strong>Languages</strong>: TypeScript, Go, Python, and Rust</li>
              <li>âš¡ <strong>Runtimes</strong>: Node.js, Bun, Deno, and serverless/edge computing</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
