              <li>ğŸ“ <strong>Database-Powered</strong>: Content stored in distributed libSQL database (Turso)</li>
              <li>ğŸ” <strong>Semantic Search</strong>: AI-powered vector search for intelligent content discovery</li>
              <li>ğŸš€ <strong>Edge-Ready</strong>: Fast global access with automatic replication</li>
